{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"594e6e6313","title":"中共中央关于党员党籍处理问题的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"194faebc2d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":12,"articleId":"594e6e6313"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3df4ae75e1","name":"干部和干部政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"91736a0628","name":"中共中央通知","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3d36628534","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于党员党籍处理问题的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"},{"id":"06ad58dbda","type":"paragraph","text":"各级党委、各级军区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"},{"id":"2fa2f594af","type":"paragraph","text":"最近，有些单位的党组织或群众组织按照某些群众的要求，开除了一些党员的党籍，有的还当场烧毁了入党志愿书等档案材料。对此，中央认为：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"},{"id":"7d7d521321","type":"paragraph","text":"一、除了逮捕法办的现行反革命分子应该立即开除其党籍外，一般党员的党籍处理，应该放在运动后期进行。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"},{"id":"67551b1b7d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、按照党章规定，党员的处分，必须由党组织执行，群众及其组织，无权对党员进行党纪处分。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"},{"id":"660173bc72","type":"paragraph","text":"三、有关党员的入党申请书等档案材料，不得烧毁。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"},{"id":"645d01acc2","type":"paragraph","text":"这个通知可以在农村、城市和部队各单位内普遍张贴。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"},{"id":"1cd19d059f","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"},{"id":"9089ae2c37","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年二月十二日","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313"}],"page":{"id":"d3744fc79c","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"594e6e6313","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}